Literally everything has an equivalent in the cell, in the body, in the cosmos etc. The only reason the microscopic world is not filled with symbolic meaning is because it was discovered too late, it is up to us to do this. I think often about this
One time a girl came into my room and saw my schizo drawings of random organs/cells etc. with names of Biblical cities written on them

Important to note that this  represents the lowest level of ourselves - the vices, seven sins, the lack of mercy, everything related to the snake-like primordial spine. But we can also, seemingly against nature, go against these instincts - why and how? There is something else.
